race.comment: WINNING REVOLUTION (3) is a mainstay in these high benchmark sprint races in SA and again he looks a great winning chance here. He's won three and placed seven at the track and distance. He will get back but he'll be finishing hard and he can win. WIGGUM (2) is a class sprinter with a brilliant first-up record and must come into consideration. SIXTEEN REASONS (1) drops in grade after sound midfield efforts here in far stronger company. Won't know herself back to this level. MT NISEKO (7) is flying with consecutive wins at this course in lesser company. Should land in a good spot from the low draw and gets his chance to make it three wins in a row.
